SAUCE: (TOMATOES (TOMATO, SALT, CITRIC ACID), OREGANO, BASIL, SUGAR, GARLIC POWDER, SALT, RED PEPPER FLAKES) CITRIC ACID USED FOR FLAVOR. SEASONED GROUND BEEF CRUMBLES: BEEF, SALT, FLAVORING, CARAMEL COLOR.
